## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [etfqo-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Reduced female fertile. No phenotype when grown in short days.
   - [etfqo-2]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Reduced female fertile. Normal phenotype when grown under short/long days. When grown in the dark after 10 days early senescence followed by death.
   - [etfqo-3]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Reduced female fertile in short days. In dark ,plants show early sensecence and die before wild type sibs.
